technique要識"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T12:15:50.000Z","msg":"我當初第一次聽佢彈嗰陣真係以為聽緊個professional喺度彈緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢個世界真係有天才呢樣嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />只不過唔係我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8056fcdbe0f554012436008f2dca478881a8f8cc","tid":2137104,"uid":72241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T12:44:53.000Z","msg":"有興趣可以傾吓<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lightbulb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/emstiolleh\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Femstiolleh&d=Surr%2FXenqJySG8qcND35%2F%2FsPRfgRtgRFNgQ5kFpanIU%3D&h=a7b93313\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/emstiolleh</a>"},{"pid":"b69952a2a57191bfde843fa46ee3e1e7354b861f","tid":2137104,"uid":263409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9c9528596628b2b49be75b9bae6152626c337871","tid":2137104,"uid":251872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b3f6f21b1d2e97ceb9f54ca5a10f3b1221a08061","tid":2137104,"uid":134683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T16:01:34.000Z","msg":"淺既譜係可以自學<br />\n深既又唔係唔得<br />\n但會彈壞手勢錯哂指法<br />\n到你想學彈其他譜就會好難彈得好<br />\n而且彈壞手勢好多人都改唔到<br />\n所以最好初級已經要跟人學"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T16:02:59.000Z","msg":"原來係咁 大概幾耐會學到一級?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T12:51:39.000Z","msg":"唔好比個「級」限制自己。<br />\n好多人自學到識飛，例如彈jazz或者pop嘢個d人，耳仔聽音好，手指又夠快，除非你想學正統古典音樂彈法，否則只要彈到就話之你幾多「級」。"},{"pid":"208746e8e668c0cf194c378c5f0d290987d2b5bc","tid":2137104,"uid":251872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cc5260c52653e60231fc008df795ecf61e0a5a61","tid":2137104,"uid":39734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ccb0b855d13390bae4ad1704a45de55e706248b4","tid":2137104,"uid":364611,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"0c02bea145ab4772258df0e6ce28960d5b